  "instructions": [
    "Heat the score-fat in the tagine pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the pine nuts and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the yeast, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 1 cup of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional pine nuts if desired."
